OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cofficers who Pava-sprayed and tasered
OL,5,Camputee
OL,7,FThe jury in the trial of two police
OL,8,Fofficers who Pava-sprayed and tasered
OL,9,Fa 92-year-old amputee while responding
OL,10,Fto a call at his care home has retired
OL,11,Fto begin deliberations.
OL,13,FPc Stephen Smith, 51, and Pc Rachel
OL,14,FComotto, 36, faced trial at Southwark
OL,15,FCrown Court accused of using excessive
OL,16,Fforce on Donald Burgess during an
OL,17,Fincident at Park Beck care home in St
OL,18,FLeonards-on-Sea, East Sussex, in June
OL,19,F2022.
