OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cofficers who Pava-sprayed and tasered
OL,5,Camputee
OL,7,FThe care home had called 999 after Mr
OL,8,FBurgess, a single-leg amputee and
OL,9,Fwheelchair user, reportedly grabbed a
OL,10,Fknife and threatened to stab staff.
OL,12,FJudge Christopher Hehir, summarising
OL,13,Fthe evidence on Wednesday, told
OL,14,Fjurors: "The reason for his behaviour
OL,15,Fthat day, we now know, is that he was
OL,16,Fdelirious as a result of a urinary
OL,17,Ftract infection."
