OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cofficers who Pava-sprayed and tasered
OL,5,Camputee
OL,7,FSmith sprayed synthetic Pava pepper
OL,8,Fspray into Mr Burgess's face and
OL,9,Fstruck his wrist with a baton, with
OL,10,FComotto deploying her Taser, all
OL,11,Fwithin a minute and 23 seconds of
OL,12,Fentering the wheelchair-bound
OL,13,Fpensioner's room.
OL,15,FSmith denies two counts of assault
OL,16,Foccasioning actual bodily harm for his
OL,17,Fuse of Pava spray and for using a
OL,18,Fbaton, whilst Comotto denies one count
OL,19,Frelated to her use of a Taser on Mr
OL,20,FBurgess.
