OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cofficers who Pava-sprayed and tasered
OL,5,Camputee
OL,7,FJudge Hehir asked jurors to retire and
OL,8,Fconsider their verdicts on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fadding they should reach their
OL,10,Fdecision "with their heads, not their
OL,11,Fhearts".
OL,13,FProsecutors say the force used against
OL,14,FMr Burgess, who had been reportedly
OL,15,Fwaving the serrated cutlery knife
OL,16,Faround and telling staff he would
OL,17,F"take pleasure" in murdering them, was
OL,18,F"unjustified and unlawful" given his
OL,19,Fage and physical condition.
