OL,7,FMr Burgess was taken to hospital after
OL,8,Fthe incident and later contracted
OL,9,FCovid.
OL,11,FHe died 22 days later aged 93.
OL,13,FSmith previously told jurors he did
OL,14,Fnot see that Mr Burgess was disabled
OL,15,Fand using a wheelchair as he was
OL,16,Ffocused on the knife the pensioner was
OL,17,Fholding in his hand.
