OL,7,FDuring her evidence, Comotto said she
OL,8,Fbelieved using the Taser was the
OL,9,Fsafest way to "protect" Mr Burgess as
OL,10,Fshe feared her colleague using the
OL,11,Fbaton again would cause more harm.
OL,13,F"I'm not a trigger-happy officer," she
OL,14,Ftold jurors.
OL,16,F"It's the first time I've fired my
OL,17,FTaser."
